node.text: @nicolelapin is joining @wearewarriors for our “What the finance!” course where Nicole will be doing multiple live calls to break down the taboos of spending, saving, earning, investing and more. I’m so grateful she’s coming on because this is the knowledge I would have loved to have as a teenager. Join us for this course on www.wearewarriors.co

node.text:
Last video of my trip with Coral gardeners. I am so grateful for this experience. It wasn't easy, but it was absolutely worth it. Thank you so much for everyone who donated. We're 16k away from our 100k goal. Please spread the word so we can make even more of an impact!! @coralgardeners 
www.gofundme.com/f/alexisren

node.text: I postponed uploading this video for the last week because it was so hard for me to record. All I ask is for you to be soft about this subject. my hope is that a few of you can resonate with what I’m saying and I can help your healing process. It’s not easy, but we don’t have to do it alone

node.text: This has been a topic I've been wanting to speak about, and I'm grateful that you want to hear my story and what I've learned from dealing with an ED. I don't have all the answers, but just like you, I strive to be a better version of myself and to grow every day. I hope this helps you.

node.text: I'm so grateful that this is my life, and that I'm able to share it. I may not always get things right, but I strive to be a better, stronger, human for each and every one of you. Thank you for standing by me and watching me grow into the woman I am today. 2019 ain't ready for us :)

node.text: Thank you to Dancing With The Stars for letting me express my love for my mother who passed away in 2014 due to cancer. This was her favorite show and I am so grateful to get the opportunity to dedicate a dance to her. Straight from my heart x

node.text: I love connecting with all of you, and for those of you I’ve touched I’m so grateful I did because that’s my purpose- to help you feel closer to you, to help you understand connection comes first, not the opportunity or the dream. If you follow alignment with others your dreams come like building a sand castle. Fun, easy, exciting. Life is an endless synchronized harmony if you commit to the lessons, not the answers. I have a lot of faith in our generation, I have a lot of faith in earth. I know this whole thing is really overwhelming and we’re all questioning what the point of any of this is, but I swear that’s the beauty in it. It’s your choice. Enjoy your paradox because as soon as we come into this life we’re slowly but surely leaving it. All the mundane bullshit we put up with is god asking us to fall in love over and over again. To remember. We’re all just here for each other.

node.text: July 2021 has a special place in my heart. thank you to everyone that was part of this crew and helped make this film so special! a week before I got the call I was writing in my journal thanking spirit and giving god permission to move me to the  next phase in my evolution. And bam, the universe delivered. So if you feel discouraged about your manifestations not happening, don’t let that stop you from feeling gratitude. Give the universe permission to lead you, because i promise it wants too. Like for real spirit…you do it. I call shotgun
